351
00:27:25,980 --> 00:27:27,260
onto you.

352
00:27:30,180 --> 00:27:31,460
But I have to say

353
00:27:31,820 --> 00:27:33,740
that your temper is unpredictable,

354
00:27:33,900 --> 00:27:34,780
and I've been disoriented

355
00:27:34,780 --> 00:27:36,580
by your confusing instructions
along the journey.

356
00:27:37,660 --> 00:27:39,900
You told me
you were going home for a funeral.

357
00:27:40,340 --> 00:27:41,460
But it turned out you came to see Xu...

358
00:27:49,540 --> 00:27:50,380
Ms. Wang.

359
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:52,140
Are we here

360
00:27:52,420 --> 00:27:53,700
to visit Xu Youguang especially?

361
00:28:03,260 --> 00:28:04,020
Feng Tianlan.

362
00:28:06,980 --> 00:28:09,060
Every person has an irreparable memory

363
00:28:09,620 --> 00:28:11,260
and something they intend to avoid.

364
00:28:12,060 --> 00:28:13,460
So, can I choose not to tell?

365
00:28:25,660 --> 00:28:26,460
Ms. Wang.

366
00:28:39,460 --> 00:28:39,860
Okay.

367
00:28:40,340 --> 00:28:41,540
Forget about the past.

368
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:43,500
Let's go on.

369
00:28:44,380 --> 00:28:45,020
Let's do this.

370
00:28:48,620 --> 00:28:50,100
(Mr. Wu)

371
00:28:56,060 --> 00:28:56,900
Hello.

372
00:28:57,660 --> 00:28:58,460
Yes.

373
00:28:58,940 --> 00:29:00,180
